Destination ahead 5.3 miles.

541
00:32:35,150 --> 00:32:38,610
Home is ahead one-quarter mile.

542
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:40,340
Home?

543
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:42,840
Right turn ahead.

544
00:32:42,850 --> 00:32:45,660
Turn right now.

545
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:55,450
