546
00:32:59,450 --> 00:33:01,870
You are home.

547
00:33:06,190 --> 00:33:08,770
Not my home.

548
00:33:11,980 --> 00:33:14,110
Oh,my gosh!

549
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:17,000
Turn right now.

550
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:21,810
Wait. What are you talking
about? Turn right where?

551
00:33:21,820 --> 00:33:24,840
Turn right now.

552
00:33:30,180 --> 00:33:33,550
Turn right now.

553
00:33:38,330 --> 00:33:42,740
